      "content": "Okay, that sounds a lot more manageable. If we can just handle it with the WAF and some live patching, we avoid the massive outage. Just to be 100% sure before I sign off on this—is there any scenario where this vulnerability could actually lead to a full data breach if we don't do the emergency maintenance? I need to know if I'm potentially ignoring a massive security hole here.",
